= Minimal Plot Test

== Test 1: Load ggplot2

```{r}
#| eval: true
#| echo: true
#| output: true
library(ggplot2)
print("ggplot2 loaded")
```

== Test 2: Create and export plot

```{r}
#| eval: true
#| echo: true
#| output: true
gg <- ggplot(iris, aes(x = Sepal.Length, y = Sepal.Width)) +
  geom_point()

typst(gg)
```

== Test 3: Verify session persists

```{r}
#| eval: true
#| echo: true
#| output: true
print(paste("ggplot2 still loaded:", "ggplot2" %in% (.packages())))
```
